<!-- Tutorial steps -->
<div class="container">

  <p class="mt-3">Now that you have a Maven project in the <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong>, 
    let's create a simple Java app that uses the <a href="http://salesforce-marketingcloud.github.io/FuelSDK-Java/" target="_blank">Marketing Cloud Java SDK</a> to test the connection to Marketing Cloud.</p>

  <p class="mt-3">The Java app uses pre-provisioned API Keys (<code>Client ID</code> and <code>Client Secret</code>) from the <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> environment to connect to Marketing Cloud.</p>

  <form id="formRunCommand" action="/playgound-api/java/runapp1" method="post">
 
    <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-block">
        <div class="card-header text-white" style="background-color: #00AA9E;">Test connection to Marketing Cloud</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Click <strong>Compile and Run Java app</strong> to run the app in the playground and test the connection to Marketing Cloud.</p>

          <p class="card-text">Lines <code>9 and 10</code> in the code below use the <code>Client ID</code> and <code>Client Secret</code> from the <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground</strong> environment.</p>
          <button id="buttonRun" class="btn btn-secondary" type="submit">Compile and Run Java app</button>
          
          <pre style="max-height: 30em" class="line-numbers" data-line="9-10" data-src="/code-snippets/java/app1-playground.java"></pre>
            <div class="card mt-3">
              <div class="card-header"><small>CONSOLE OUTPUT</small></div>
              <pre style="max-height: 30em" class="m-2">
                <code id="textRunOutput" class="language-bash">Nothing yet. Click 'Compile and Run Java App' to see results.</code>
              </pre>
            </div>

            <div id="textSuccess" class="hide-element">
              <p class="card-text mt-3"><span class="fa fa-star text-success"></span>&nbsp;You have sucessfully compiled and run a simple Java app in the <strong>Marketing Cloud SDK Playground!</strong></p>
              <p class="card-text"><span class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up text-success"></span>&nbsp;You're ready to try an advanced Java app!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  </form>
</div>

